## 7. Invoice Pipeline ŌĆö The Billing Brain

### Full Flow
```
Upload carrier CSV/XLSX in The Alamo
        Ōåō
AI normalizes headers ŌåÆ Cactus Standard fields
        Ōåō
Human review queue
        Ōåō
For each line item:
  IF lassoed:
    Match tracking_number ŌåÆ shipment_ledger ŌåÆ org_id
    Compare carrier_charge vs quoted_rate
    IF variance > dispute_threshold ŌåÆ HELD + dispute_flag
    ELSE ŌåÆ apply markup ŌåÆ Single-Ceiling ŌåÆ APPROVED

  IF dark:
    Normalize ship_from_address
    Match ŌåÆ locations.normalized_address (is_billing_address=TRUE)
    IF one match ŌåÆ assign org ŌåÆ markup ŌåÆ Single-Ceiling
    IF zero/multiple ŌåÆ FLAGGED ŌåÆ manual review
    Create shipment_ledger row (shipment_source = INVOICE_IMPORT)
        Ōåō
Generate cactus_invoices from APPROVED line items
        Ōåō
Sync to QuickBooks Online
```

### Address Normalization Format
`"1234 MAIN ST, PHOENIX, AZ, 85001, US"`
Uppercase. Abbreviated street type. State abbreviation.

