## 11. Coding Philosophy

- WHY comments on every non-obvious block
- Rate card failure never halts label production
- Idempotency keys on all label purchases and meter reloads
- Async Shadow Ledger writes ŌĆö never block rating response
- Graceful carrier API error handling ŌĆö never fail entire response
- Performance: Rating < 500ms, Label < 2000ms, Dashboard < 1s

