## 12. Security Standards
- API keys in `.env` only ŌĆö never hardcoded
- `.env` in `.gitignore` ŌĆö never committed
- Payment tokens only ŌĆö raw card data never in Cactus
- Service role key ŌĆö backend only, never in browser
- All timestamps: `TIMESTAMPTZ`

