## 14. DESIGN SYSTEM ŌĆö THE ALAMO & CACTUS PORTAL

### Design Philosophy
Crisp lines. Clean spacing. Less noise. Detail-oriented.
Stripe-level data density for The Alamo.
Apple-level restraint for the Cactus Portal.
Same system, different spacing expression.
No pure black. No shadows. No gradients. Always 0.5px borders.

### The Three Brand Colors
Forest  #2D5A27 ŌĆö operational, active, confirmed, primary CTA
Amber   #D97706 ŌĆö client-facing warmth, savings highlights, Portal CTA
Bloom   #D81B7A ŌĆö warnings, disputes, held items, attention required

The cactus in full expression:
  Forest = the plant. Grounded, alive, resilient.
  Amber  = the desert sun. Warm, energetic, inviting.
  Bloom  = the flower. Striking, urgent, beautiful.

### Full Color Token Set
--cactus-forest:       #2D5A27  primary brand, buttons, links, active nav
--cactus-mint:         #EEF4EB  green surface, active nav bg, approved badges
--cactus-forest-deep:  #1A3D15  green badge text

--cactus-amber:        #D97706  vibrant amber, Portal CTA, savings highlights
--cactus-amber-bg:     #FEF3C7  amber surface
